WEBVTT

00:08:59.800 --> 00:09:02.456
our faith not just
in the context of religion,

00:09:02.480 --> 00:09:06.176
but our faith in politicians
and tribe and nation,

00:09:06.200 --> 00:09:09.880
our faith in the older generation
and in the younger generation.

00:09:11.360 --> 00:09:15.216
